TITLE: Success Toast with Check Icon with EUI
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the proper way to use an icon within a toast message, reinforcing the action's success. The style prop is used to set the max width.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/display/toast/_guidelines.mdx#_snippet_10

