TITLE: Data Grid Trailing Control Columns
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the trailing control columns for the EuiDataGrid. It includes a header cell that displays 'Controls' for screen readers only. The row cell renderer manages the visibility of EuiPopover, EuiModal, and EuiFlyout components, providing examples of interactive elements within the grid.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/tabular-content/data-grid/data-grid.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: tsx
