TITLE: Customizing EuiComment with different props - React/TSX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to customize the EuiComment component with different props to create various types of comment events. It includes examples for regular comments, updates, and custom comments, showcasing the flexibility of the component. It uses EuiButtonGroup to toggle between different comment types and EuiSelect to choose a color to use for the event. The component imports and leverages EuiTextArea, EuiCommentList, EuiComment, EuiButtonGroup, EuiButtonIcon, EuiText, EuiBadge, EuiFlexGroup, EuiFlexItem, EuiSpacer, EuiCommentListProps, EuiSelect, EuiCode, and EuiCommentEventProps from the @elastic/eui package.
