TITLE: Implementing Column Layout with Compressed EUI Forms in React
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement a two-column layout for compressed forms using EUI (Elastic UI Framework) and React. It utilizes the `display="columnCompressed"` prop within the EuiFormRow component to align labels and inputs side by side. It showcases various form elements like EuiFieldText, EuiSelect, EuiFilePicker, EuiComboBox, EuiRange and EuiSwitch. It manages the state of the form elements using React's `useState` hook and provides event handlers to update the state.
