TITLE: Implementing EuiPopover Component with React
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement the EuiPopover component using React and Typescript. It includes managing the popover's visibility state, rendering a button to toggle the popover, and defining the content to be displayed within the popover. The component uses EuiButtonEmpty and EuiText components from the @elastic/eui library. The popover automatically closes when clicking outside its bounds.
