TITLE: EuiDataGrid focus and interactive cells - React (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the focus management of the `EuiDataGrid` component, specifically when cells contain interactive elements.  It creates a data grid with columns containing varying numbers of interactive elements (links, buttons) and demonstrates how the `EuiDataGrid` manages focus for keyboard and screen reader accessibility. Uses `EuiButtonIcon`, `EuiLink`, `EuiBadge`, `EuiToken`, `EuiFlexGroup`, `EuiFlexItem`, `EuiTextColor` components.
