TITLE: Key/Value Form with Labels (EUI)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows a better alternative to using placeholders as labels. It uses EuiFormRow with explicit labels "Key" and "Value" for the input fields, providing clear and accessible labeling. A button is included to "Add" the key-value pair.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/forms/controls/guidelines.mdx#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: html
