TITLE: Constraining Popover - EuiPopover with Container Prop in React
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases how to constrain an EuiPopover within a specific container element. The `container` prop accepts a React or DOM element.  It utilizes `EuiPanel` and `panelRef` for container management. The popover is positioned using the `downCenter` placement but is restricted to fit within the panel.
