TITLE: Sparkline Implementation with EUI and Elastic Charts
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet implements sparklines using EUI components (like `EuiPanel`, `EuiStat`, `EuiFlexGrid`) and Elastic Charts.  It demonstrates how to create different types of sparklines (Bar, Line, Area) with custom theming, data handling, and styling based on dark or light mode. It includes configurations for hiding legends and tooltips.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/dataviz/sizing.mdx#_snippet_1

