TITLE: EuiDatePicker Locale Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to configure the locale formatting for the EuiDatePicker component.  It uses the `locale`, `timeFormat`, and `dateFormat` props to customize the date and time display based on different locales. It requires React, EuiDatePicker, EuiFormRow, EuiSpacer, and moment. The comments highlights the dynamic locale loading of moment.
