TITLE: EuiFlyout without ownFocus
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to create an EuiFlyout without obscuring the underlying page content using the `ownFocus={false}` prop.  This allows users to interact with elements beneath the flyout while it is open.  The flyout's visibility is toggled using React's `useState`.
