TITLE: Rendering EuiCommentList with EuiMarkdownEditor
DESCRIPTION: This section renders the EuiCommentList component, displaying the list of comments and a markdown editor for adding new comments. The EuiMarkdownEditor is configured with a placeholder, value, onChange handler, and a readOnly state based on the loading state, and uses markdownFormatProps to set text size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/display/comment-list/index.mdx#_snippet_8

