TITLE: Creating Sunburst and Treemap Charts with Elastic Charts
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the creation of sunburst and treemap charts using Elastic Charts within a React component. It utilizes the `GITHUB_DATASET_MOD` dataset. The code configures the charts with custom color palettes (`useEuiPaletteColorBlind`) and theming from `useChartBaseTheme`. The `Partition` component is used with different `PartitionLayout` values (sunburst and treemap) to create the charts. The snippet showcases hierarchical data visualization with customizable legends and data groupings.
