TITLE: Single Value Metric Chart Example (React/Elastic Charts)
DESCRIPTION: This React component demonstrates the usage of the Elastic Charts Metric component to display a single value with custom formatting and color coding.  It uses EuiRange to control the value and updates the Metric chart based on the selected range. The valueFormatter is configured to format the number as currency.  Dependencies: @elastic/charts, @elastic/eui.
