TITLE: FormControlLayout with EuiFieldText in React
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases various configurations of the `EuiFormControlLayout` component in conjunction with `EuiFieldText`. It demonstrates how to utilize the `icon`, `isLoading`, `clear`, `isInvalid`, `prepend`, and `append` props to style and enhance form controls.  It requires the `EuiFormControlLayout`, `EuiFormLabel`, `EuiButtonEmpty`, `EuiText`, `useGeneratedHtmlId`, `useEuiTheme`, and `EuiFieldText` components from the `@elastic/eui` library. The example utilizes the `controlOnly` prop of `EuiFieldText` to control its rendering within the layout.
