TITLE: Adding a Banner to EuiFlyout
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to add a banner to an EuiFlyout using the `banner` prop of the EuiFlyoutBody component.  The banner utilizes the EuiCallOut component to display important information.  The example manages the flyout's visibility using React's `useState` hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/containers/flyout/index.mdx#_snippet_5

