TITLE: Closing Popover in EuiTable
DESCRIPTION: This function closes the actions popover for a specific item. It updates the state with a new `itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap` where the visibility of the popover is set to false for the given item.  It only updates the state if the popover is currently open.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/tabular-content/tables/custom.mdx#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
closePopover = (itemId: number) => {
    // only update the state if this item's popover is open
    if (this.isPopoverOpen(itemId)) {
      this.setState((previousState) => {
        const newItemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap = {
          ...previousState.itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap,
          [itemId]: false,
        };

        return {
          itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap: newItemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap,
        };
      });
    }
  };
```

