TITLE: Implementing ColorPicker with Custom Button and Secondary Input (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases the usage of a custom button as a trigger for color selection in the `EuiColorPicker` component using the `button` prop. It also demonstrates the use of the `secondaryInputDisplay` prop to show an alternative color value input. The example uses `EuiColorPickerSwatch` and `EuiBadge` as custom buttons, and manages the color state using the `useColorPickerState` hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/forms/other/color-picker.mdx#_snippet_7

