TITLE: Custom Table Implementation with EUI Components in React
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the creation of a custom table using various EUI components. It includes defining interfaces for data and columns, managing state for selection and pagination, and rendering the table with features like sorting, filtering (though not explicitly implemented in the code), and mobile responsiveness. It relies on @elastic/eui library and utilizes React.
