TITLE: Selecting Colors with Automatic Format in EuiColorPicker
DESCRIPTION: This example illustrates the default behavior of `EuiColorPicker` where it automatically uses the last input value format. It uses the `useColorPickerState` hook to manage the color state and displays the `EuiColorPicker` component within an `EuiFormRow` to show potential validation errors.
