TITLE: Completely Customizing Cell Popover Rendering - EUI Data Grid (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates complete customization of the cell popover rendering using the `renderCellPopover` prop. It defines a `RenderCellPopover` component that receives props such as `children`, `cellContentsElement`, `cellActions`, `DefaultCellPopover`, and `setCellPopoverProps` to allow full control over the popover's content and appearance. The example showcases conditional popover content based on schema, custom cell actions, and fallback to the default popover rendering.
