TITLE: EuiSelectable in Popover & Flyout (React/TS)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates integrating EuiSelectable within EuiPopover and EuiFlyout components. It showcases how to manage the visibility state of the popover and flyout using React's useState hook.  The SelectablePopover and SelectableFlyout components encapsulate the EuiSelectable functionality within their respective containers, providing a clear separation of concerns.
