TITLE: Using EuiCopy Component
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the EuiCopy component to copy text from an EuiFieldText component to the clipboard when a button is clicked. It uses React's useState hook to manage the text to be copied.  It imports EuiCopy, EuiButton, EuiFieldText, EuiSpacer, and EuiFormRow from '@elastic/eui'.
