TITLE: Implementing EuiOutsideClickDetector in React
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to use the EuiOutsideClickDetector component in a React application.  It creates a component with a button to enable/disable the click detector and a paragraph that displays a message based on the detector's state.  When enabled, clicking outside the paragraph triggers an alert.
