TITLE: Incorrect Child CSS Merging Example (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates an incorrect way of merging CSS props for child elements using Emotion CSS.  It highlights the issue where Emotion will not automatically merge `css` props passed via `childProps` (e.g., `iconProps`) into the child component.  This can lead to unintended style overrides or ignoring of the child's CSS.
