TITLE: EuiDataGrid Footer Cell Rendering
DESCRIPTION: Defines a custom footer cell renderer function (`RenderFooterCellValue`) that receives a column ID. It retrieves the corresponding value from the `footerCellValues` object and renders it. If the value is empty, it disables cell expansion.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/tabular-content/data-grid/schema-and-columns.mdx#_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const RenderFooterCellValue = ({ columnId, setCellProps }) => {
  const value = footerCellValues[columnId];

  useEffect(() => {
    // Turn off the cell expansion button if the footer cell is empty
    if (!value) setCellProps({ isExpandable: false });
  }, [value, setCellProps]);

  return value || null;
};
```

