TITLE: Configuring Cypress Axe
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to configure `cy.checkAxe()` with custom rulesets and settings.  It imports a default Axe configuration, extends it with a custom rule, and then passes the custom configuration to `cy.checkAxe()`. This allows for more specific accessibility testing.
