TITLE: Toggling Popover Visibility in EuiTable
DESCRIPTION: This function toggles the visibility of the actions popover for a specific item. It updates the state with a new `itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap` where the visibility of the popover is inverted for the given item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/tabular-content/tables/custom.mdx#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
togglePopover = (itemId: number) => {
    this.setState((previousState) => {
      const newItemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap = {
        ...previousState.itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap,
        [itemId]: !previousState.itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap[itemId],
      };

      return {
        itemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap: newItemIdToOpenActionsPopoverMap,
      };
    });
  };
```

