TITLE: Displaying a Grid of Tokens
DESCRIPTION: This snippet iterates through an array of `iconTypes` and renders each as an EuiToken inside of an EuiFlexGrid. The `iconType` prop of the EuiToken determines which icon is displayed. The type name is also rendered below the icon, wrapped in an EuiCopy component for easy copying.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/eui/blob/main/packages/website/docs/components/display/icons/index.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
